6, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"my teammates\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"my mom\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think it's even more special - even now I get emotional thinking about it - that so many incredible people just think that I am worth of this.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"emotional thinking\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"so many incredible people\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It means a lot, truly,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flag bearers are selected by vote from fellow Team USA athletes, with Gauff nominated by tennis star and close friend Chris Eubanks.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1344, \"end\": 1352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9998750139700227, \"rank\": 0.00011460238158570157, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Flag bearers\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"vote\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"Gauff\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis star\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"close friend Chris Eubanks\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am incredibly proud of Coco - I know how great she is as a tennis player, but more importantly, how great she is as a person,\\\" Eubanks said in a statement.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coco\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"a tennis player\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ng